_sText:
this map was made in a day and a half. it is rushed and used uh A LOT of unethical mapping methods. This map was done since early january but only decided to post it now for no particular reasons...

Features:
-Broken NAV mesh making hostage rescue impossible (you'll got to remove the bad guys regardless)
-Raid-style map
-Extremely terrorists sided. If you're CT, You're fucked.
-OP basement for terrorists. again, if you're CT. You're fucked.
-No 3D skybox so here's some realistic scenery for 1996
-Extremely wallbangable map. You can buy m249 on CT side to fight with the Ts op-ness.
-Cool features mentioned above.

I will not "fix" the "problems" you may have with the map. if you find one then I can guarantee you it is an intended feature.
